sequenceDiagram
    actor WielkiMistrz
    participant UI
    participant SearchView
    participant SearchService
    participant DB

    WielkiMistrz ->> UI: Open search
    WielkiMistrz ->> UI: Enter email / organization name

    UI ->> SearchView: GET /search?q=...
    SearchView ->> SearchService: search(query)

    SearchService ->> DB: full-text search
    DB -->> SearchService: results

    SearchService -->> SearchView: aggregated results
    SearchView -->> UI: render results

    UI -->> WielkiMistrz: display organization data